WORDPRESS THEME LOCATIONS
  Always look for Support and Documentation for help setting up themes before purchasing them. 
    Don't buy themes that don't have support/documentation

Some themes are more complex than others.

When purchasing themes, the theme will be downloaded as a .zip file. 
  Inside of WordPress -> Appearance -> Themes -> Add New -> Upload zipped Theme


FREE THEMES

WordPress.org
All themes here are free.


PREMIUM THEMES

Theme Companies
  Companies that make themes sell them on their website

Theme Marketplaces
  With many developer's themes for purchase
  
Individual Developer Sites
  People who create themes to sell them will show them on their own website or on their GitHub  
